<div class=3D"mw-heading mw-heading3"><h3 id=3D"Conflict_zones">Conflict zo=
nes</h3></div>
<p>When a war takes place, one or more areas within a country or across bor=
der becomes a war zone or conflict zone. Daily life is interrupted, travel =
to or across the area may be difficult and international visitors may be ad=
vised to leave the area.<sup id=3D"cite_ref-56" class=3D"reference"><a href=
=3D"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/War#cite_note-56"><span class=3D"cite-bra=
cket">[</span>55<span class=3D"cite-bracket">]</span></a></sup>
</p>
